# Email Configuration for Contact Form
# 
# IMPORTANT: To use the contact form, you need to set up a Gmail App Password:
#
# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Gmail account (3digitallfactory@gmail.com)
# 2. Go to: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Create a new App Password for "Mail"
# 4. Copy the 16-character password and paste it below
